Streams interfaces and utility classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StreamChannel<OUT>
    Interface defining a stream output channel, that is, a channel concatenating map and reduce functions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractStreamChannel<OUT>
    Abstract implementation of a stream output channel.
    Streams
    Utility class acting as a factory of stream output channels.

    Consumer implementation generating a range of data.
